Package: kyro-downloader
Version: 1.0.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.9), python3-pip, ffmpeg
Maintainer: nkpendyam <nkpendyam@users.noreply.github.com>
Description: Production-grade media downloader with 4 UI modes
 Kyro Downloader is a cross-platform media downloader supporting 20+ platforms
 with CLI, TUI, Web UI, and Desktop GUI. Features include 8K/4K HDR video,
 Dolby Atmos audio, parallel downloads, queue management, and more.
Homepage: https://github.com/nkpendyam/kyro_downloader
